data.description: Beautiful house, land, and community. New A/C and heater unit with ionizer to clean the air. Workshop 10x20'. Irrigation system linked to the well. Fruit and berry trees. Three large raised beds with organic soil. RV site with dump, water, and electricity. Beautiful hardwood floors. Reverse Osmosis water system in kitchen. Lots of parking. Completely fenced backyard with a dog door to make having pets easier. Close to shopping and Suwannee emergency room. Large and open spaciousness. Pool is a mineral pool which uses less chlorine and is easier on the body. Large sectional couch in the family room stays with the house. It still looks new after only a couple of years. Other furniture can stay if needed.
